0023#STR0023#ALL#Physical -
0024#STR0024#ALL#Noises, vibrations, ionic or non-ionic radiation, cold, heat, uncommon pressure and humidity.
0025#STR0025#ALL#Chemical -
0026#STR0026#ALL#Dust, smoke, fog, haze, gases, steam, substances, coumpounds or chemical products in general.
0027#STR0027#ALL#Biological -
